title: Katy Perry and Selena Gomez's make-up artist Jake Bailey found dead
text: He also styled the likes of Mariah Carey, Katie Holmes, Kyra Sedgwick and Jenna Dewan Tatum, while his clients have also included Nina Dobrev, Paris Hilton and Lea Michele. "Shameless" star Emmy Rossum has taken to Twitter to mourn the loss of her friend. Â»
